Titolo: Puyo Puyo Tetris 2

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Puyo Puyo Tetris 2 is a puzzle video game developed by Sonic Team and published by Sega. It is a direct sequel to Puyo Puyo Tetris. The game was released for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S on December 8, 2020  with a Microsoft Windows version released on March 21, 2021. The game released to positive reviews.